description:
AT LAST: THE BEST OF ETTA JAMES (2010)

Etta James is one of the world's greatest soul
and R&B singers. Her career spans from the hey-
day of doo-wop in the mid 50s through to her
arrival at Chess Records in 1960 right up until
present day. She is best known for her amazing
track At Last, which she made her signature tune.
On this album, At Last - The Best Of Etta James,
we  visit all her most popular songs from the
silky Cry Me A River to the funky The Blues Is
My Business. All her greatest songs are here.
